>=20
> I am writing to follow up on my previous requests, as I have not yet =
received an acknowledgement or response regarding the refund of my =
accommodation expenses.
>=20
> Under the policy coverage of NZD 30,000, there is still a remaining =
balance of NZD 1,820.62. However, reimbursement has only been provided =
up to 20 November, leaving the remaining amount outstanding.
>=20
> Additionally, on 9 October I submitted a request for reimbursement of =
NZD 395.85 for emergency veterinary expenses incurred on the day of the =
fire. The cats required urgent treatment due to prolonged smoke =
exposure. To date, I have not received either reimbursement or any =
response regarding this claim.
>=20
> Furthermore, I currently require temporary storage for the furniture =
that was salvaged, as I do not yet have a permanent place to keep these =
items.
>=20
> Could you please:
>=20
> Confirm receipt of my requests
> Process the outstanding refunds as soon as possible
> Advise on coverage for temporary storage
> I would appreciate a prompt response, as these matters remain =
unresolved.
>=20
> Kind regards,
>=20
> Raffaella
